WITH SupplierAgg AS (
    SELECT s_nationkey, SUM(ps_supplycost * ps_availqty) AS total_cost
    FROM supplier
    JOIN partsupp ON s_suppkey = ps_suppkey
    GROUP BY s_nationkey
),
CustomerOrders AS (
    SELECT c_nationkey, COUNT(o_orderkey) AS order_count, SUM(o_totalprice) AS total_revenue
    FROM customer
    JOIN orders ON c_custkey = o_custkey
    GROUP BY c_nationkey
)
SELECT r.r_name AS region_name,
       n.n_name AS nation_name,
       COALESCE(c.order_count, 0) AS total_orders,
       COALESCE(c.total_revenue, 0) AS total_revenue,
       COALESCE(s.total_cost, 0) AS total_supplier_cost
FROM region r
JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey
LEFT JOIN CustomerOrders c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
LEFT JOIN SupplierAgg s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
WHERE r.r_name = 'ASIA'
ORDER BY total_orders DESC, total_supplier_cost DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."REGION_NAME", "t6"."REGION_NAME") AS "REGION_NAME", "t6"."NATION_NAME", "t6"."TOTAL_ORDERS", "t6"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t6"."TOTAL_SUPPLIER_COST"
FROM (SELECT "region"."r_name" AS "REGION_NAME", "nation"."n_name" AS "NATION_NAME", CASE WHEN "t1"."ORDER_COUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."ORDER_COUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTAL_ORDERS", CASE WHEN "t1"."TOTAL_REVENUE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."TOTAL_REVENUE" AS DECIMAL(19, 2)) ELSE 0.00 END AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTAL_COST" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTAL_COST" AS DECIMAL(19, 2)) ELSE 0.00 END AS "TOTAL_SUPPLIER_COST"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "customer"."c_nationkey" AS "C_NATIONKEY", COUNT(*) AS "ORDER_COUNT", SUM("orders"."o_totalprice") AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM "customer"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey"
GROUP BY "customer"."c_nationkey") AS "t1" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "t1"."C_NATIONKEY"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "s1"."s_nationkey" AS "S_NATIONKEY", SUM("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_COST"
